#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Introduction"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kbruch; is a small program to practice calculating with fractions and "
"percentages. Six different exercises are offered as well as a learning mode."
msgstr ""
"&kbruch; est un petit programme pour pratiquer le calcul fractionnaire et "
"les pourcentages. Six sortes d'exercices sont proposés, ainsi qu'un mode "
"d'apprentissage."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Arithmetic - in this exercise you have to solve a given fraction task. "
#| "You have to enter the numerator and the denominator. This is the main "
#| "exercise."
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Arithmetic</guilabel> - in this exercise you have to solve a given "
"fraction task. You have to enter the numerator and the denominator. This is "
"the main exercise."
msgstr ""
"Arithmétique : dans cet exercice vous devez résoudre une fraction donnée. "
"Vous devez saisir le numérateur et le dénominateur. C'est le type d'exercice "
"principal."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Comparison - in this exercise you have to compare the size of 2 given "
#| "fractions, using the symbols <guibutton>&gt;</guibutton>, <guibutton>&lt;"
#| "</guibutton> or <guibutton>=</guibutton>."
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Comparison</guilabel> - in this exercise you have to compare the "
"size of 2 given fractions, using the symbols <guibutton>&gt;</guibutton>, "
"<guibutton>&lt;</guibutton> or <guibutton>=</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Comparaison : dans cet exercice vous devez comparer la taille de 2 fractions "
"données en utilisant les symboles <guibutton>&gt;</guibutton>, "
"<guibutton>&lt;</guibutton> ou <guibutton>=</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Conversion - in this exercise you have to convert a given number into a "
#| "fraction."
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Conversion</guilabel> - in this exercise you have to convert a "
"given number into a fraction."
msgstr ""
"Conversion : dans cet exercice vous devez convertir un nombre donné en "
"fraction."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Mixed Numbers - in this exercise you have to convert a mixed number into "
#| "an improper fraction (ratio) and vice versa."
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Mixed Numbers</guilabel> - in this exercise you have to convert a "
"mixed number into an improper fraction (ratio) and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"Nombres mixtes : dans cet exercice vous devez convertir un nombre mixte en "
"fraction impropre et vice versa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Factorization - in this exercise you have to factorize a given number "
#| "into its prime factors."
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Factorization</guilabel> - in this exercise you have to factorize "
"a given number into its prime factors."
msgstr ""
"Factorisation : dans cet exercice vous devez factoriser un nombre donné en "
"facteurs premiers."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Percentage - in this exercise you have to calculate percentages."
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Percentage</guilabel> - in this exercise you have to calculate "
"percentages."
msgstr "Pourcentage : dans cet exercice vous devez calculer des pourcentages."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In each different exercise &kbruch; will generate a task and the user has to "
"solve it. The program checks the input and gives a feedback about it."
msgstr ""
"Pour chaque type d'exercices, &kbruch; produira un problème que "
"l'utilisateur devra résoudre. Le programme vérifie les réponses et réagit en "
"conséquence."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kbruch; counts how many tasks were solved at all and how many tasks were "
"solved correctly. The statistics are shown to the user."
msgstr ""
"&kbruch; compte le nombre de problèmes qui ont été posés et le nombre de "
"problèmes qui ont été résolus correctement. Les statistiques sont montrées à "
"l'utilisateur."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kbruch; is very compact and focuses on the core idea of a task generator. "
"An online help system provides context-sensitive help for the different "
"situations."
msgstr ""
"&kbruch; est très simple et se concentre sur l'idée de générer des "
"opérations à résoudre. Un système d'aide en ligne sensible au contexte vous "
"aidera dans les différentes situations."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kbruch;"
msgstr "Utiliser &kbruch;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choosing the mode: learning or exercises"
msgstr "Choix du mode : apprentissage ou exercices"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start &kbruch;, it offers you two modes: <guilabel>Exercise</"
"guilabel> which is the training mode and <guilabel>Learning</guilabel> where "
"you can understand fractions. Clicking one of the pictures will enter the "
"chosen mode. Here is a screenshot of &kbruch;'s mode choices:"
msgstr ""
"Lorsque vous démarrez &kbruch;, il vous propose deux modes : "
"<guilabel>Exercice</guilabel> qui le mode d'entraînement et "
"<guilabel>Apprentissage</guilabel> où vous pouvez comprendre les fractions. "
"Cliquer sur une des images vous fera entrer dans le mode choisi. Voici une "
"capture d'écran du choix des modes de &kbruch; :"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kbruch; mode choices</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Choix des modes de &kbruch;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kbruch; mode choices</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Choix des modes de &kbruch;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click one of the picture to choose the mode."
msgstr "Cliquez sur une des images pour choisir le mode."

