#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "All exercises take place in this screen. This ensures that &kbruch; is "
#| "easy to use even for young users! The main screen is separated into 5 "
#| "parts: <itemizedlist> <listitem><para> the menubar with the 3 menus "
